MobileRecallPortalDocumentSummary is a CompositeForm
    title is "Notice#<RecallNotice>:_<Name>"
    restrict action Pending.Delete
    restrict action Pending.CloseAsDuplicate
    restrict action Pending.NotApplicable
    restrict action Link
    restrict action Pending.Release
    restrict action ProductTransactionQuery
    Actions
        action is save
            hide when invalid
    General is a Panel
        form is MobilePortalSummary
    Products is a Panel
        list is RecallProduct set.MobilePortalSummaryRecallProducts
    Attachments is a Panel
        list is RecallNoticeReference set.MobilePortalSummaryRecallReferences
